<div class="box">2. Processing Configuration</div>

<table>
<tr>
	<td valign="top">Capture Funds:</td>
	<td valign="top">
		<select name="cc_instant_capture" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica">
		<option value=""></option>
		<option <!-- CC_INSTANT_CAPTURE_ALWAYS_SELECTED --> value="ALWAYS">Instant Capture (authorization and transfer of funds occurs at time of checkout)</option>
		<option <!-- CC_INSTANT_CAPTURE_NEVER_SELECTED -->  value="NEVER">Delayed Capture (only authorization occurs at checkout, funds transferred later by merchant)</option>
		</select>
		<div class="hint">
		WARNING: capture funds setting is a "store setting", and is shared between paypal and credit card processing configurations.
		</div>
	</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td valign="top">Confirmed Address:</td>
	<td valign="top">
		<select name="paypal_api_reqconfirmship" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica">
		<option <!-- PAYPAL_API_REQCONFIRMSHIP_0 --> value="0"> Optional</option>
		<option <!-- PAYPAL_API_REQCONFIRMSHIP_1 -->  value="1"> Required</option>
		</select>
	</td>
</tr>
